@D commons := "cross-project common" :: governance [required active]
  do   = "ai-native · english artifacts · korean response · write & implement minimally · treat .specify/memory/constitution.md as the substantive SSOT (CLAUDE.md is a Spec Kit wrapper) · use the Spec Kit pipeline (constitution → specify → plan → tasks → implement) for feature work · stacked PRs (<200 lines · 1 logical thing · gh pr create --base previous-layer)"
  dont = "prose-only · non-english artifacts · verbose · over-engineered · touch AGENTS.tape (kept dormant carry — user-request override only) · skip Spec Kit pipeline for >200-line features · large multi-purpose PRs · long-lived feature branches"
